{"tid":2498464,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"［心路歷程］考第四次棍van終於pass","createTime":"2021-04-21T07:45:15.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-21T20:45:33.000Z","uid":293018,"like":8,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c15c70fd3226cdaab9b7523655a3787e1fdc92b9","tid":2498464,"uid":293018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T07:45:15.000Z","msg":"棍van考第四次，次次肥都唔同原因，到今日終於pass左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n前後足足兩年，真係好艱辛，不斷延期延到冇心機，打定輸數諗住考埋今次就算。<br />\n<br />\n上一次考覺得自己pass到，點知肥左d奇怪野，<br />\n今次考緊覺得自己做錯野會肥，點知合格到。<br />\n可能因為自己諗住肥埋今次就算，反而冇咁緊張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望連登個個都可以一take pass，考既過程真係好痛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c8fe48c070b95cce6eec6e4ebb55e95d1f48f7d","tid":2498464,"uid":189109,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T07:47:38.000Z","msg":"小兒麻痺就唔好揸車啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d68bf0e2a6ffc070caba594528f64f5bcfe7b9d2","tid":2498464,"uid":153,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T07:48:47.000Z","msg":"唔好揸出街就得"},{"pid":"c32b5e7938ecc38b5d0bc27d5aa659f690ab080d","tid":2498464,"uid":6310,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T07:54:31.000Z","msg":"垃圾到咁都敢開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />